law.catch_line: Order in which property shall be levied on and sold.
law.text: Property shall be liable to levy and sale under execution in the following order: First, personalty; second, land.
law.history: Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1692.
